name: AIR CANADA'S "PRIVATE JET?" Flying an Empty A330 from Toronto to Montreal
description:
In February, I had quite an interesting flight with Air Canada, on their Airbus A330! A maintenance issue, two hour delay, and aircraft swap on this evening flight resulted in one of the most unforgettable avgeek experiences I've had with Air Canada.

See what I thought of their A330 Business Class, on this short hop from Toronto to Montreal!

Better look at the IFE: https://youtu.be/C0Vm-zn4vu4?t=774
